These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: december, august, march, april, may, june, october
The people have 7 different hobbies: hiking, singing, puzzles, cooking, magic-tricks, board-games, rock-climbing
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: musical, disaster, fantasy, romance, mystery, crime, time-travel
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the person watching musical movies##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
14. the person who's birthday is in june is the person watching fantasy movies##1
15. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
19. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
| Birthday   | august | april         | october   | december | june    | may | march |
| Hobby         | puzzles | magic-tricks | hiking | singing | rock-climbing  | board-games  | cooking    |
| Movie-Genre     | mystery  | crime         | musical     | disaster    | fantasy | romance     | time-travel     |

