 1. the oliveros-smoker is the person eating pineapple##1
 2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 4. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is the havana-smoker##1
 8. the person playing billiard is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
10. the person playing canasta is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person eating strawberry##2
11. the person playing whist is the person eating pineapple##1
12. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing go##1
13. the person playing bridge is between the person eating strawberry and the person playing go##2
14. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
15. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
16. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
17. the person eating apricot is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
18. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
19. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
20. the person eating broccoli is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person eating artichoke##2

